61
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:34,810
Who are you?

62
00:05:35,370 --> 00:05:36,250
What do you want?

63
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:39,050
I'm Lu Xiuyuan's son,

64
00:05:39,570 --> 00:05:40,200
Lu Li.

65
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:41,690
I want to know

66
