92
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:10,960
Mr. Su.

93
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,760
Hi, I'm Sun Yiming.

94
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,570
Here's my card.

95
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:15,200
It's quite lively today.

96
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,760
Let's take a look over there.

97
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:20,810
Mr. Su.

98
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,440
Wish you booming business.

99
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:24,370
What a great day.

100
00:07:24,370 --> 00:07:25,200
Look at this.

101
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:27,760
The renovation here

102
00:07:28,170 --> 00:07:29,690
