106
00:07:43,690 --> 00:07:44,760
(I thought)

107
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,960
(we'd never cross paths again.)

108
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,640
(Unexpectedly, he reached out)

109
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,760
(to me after a while.)

110
00:07:51,335 --> 00:07:56,285
