Can the Art Giant Survive This?)

111
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,570
Hello?

112
00:08:06,010 --> 00:08:07,840
- Mr. Su?
- Mr. Sun, right?

113
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,960
Yes.

114
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:12,960
Okay.

115
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,250
Alright, got it.

116
00:08:15,250 --> 00:08:16,200
I'll arrive in a bit.

117
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,640
Okay.

118
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,210
(I never expected)

119
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,970
(Su Shilun contacted me)

120
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,040
(so that)

121
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,250
(an unknown financial agent)

122
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,160
(like me)

123
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,280
