124
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:43,610
(More shockingly,)

125
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,850
(the money didn't belong to him at all.)

126
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,160
(He secretly transferred it
from the Qin family)

127
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,850
(through his engagement to Qin Wanyou.)

128
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:55,370
This part will be transferred
out of the finance firm

129
00:08:55,370 --> 00:08:57,640
before going into the account
I mentioned.

130
00:08:58,090 --> 00:08:59,370
Take a look.

131
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,800
What does this mean?

132
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,960
Okay, as per your request,

133
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,490
we've done a breakdown for this part.

134
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:12,040
(Without knowing it,)

135
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,610
(I helped launder a huge sum
for Su Shilun)

136
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,560
(and made good money.)

137
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,680
(My status soared.)

138
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:19,970
(My partnership with Su Shilun)

139
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:22,250
(shifted from behind the scenes.)

140
00:09:23,210 --> 00:09:24,680
(He introduced me to many people,)

141
00:09:25,370 --> 00:09:26,640
(including)

142
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:29,400
(his best friend, Lu Xiuyuan.)

143
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,760
It's my job.

144
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:32,010
It's my job.

145
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,000
With your help,

146
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,210
I have nothing to worry about.

147
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,210
It's my job.

148
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:40,010
Let me see.

149
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,560
- I have no questions.
- Just sign here.

150
00:09:43,610 --> 00:09:44,880
It's official once signed.

151
00:09:46,210 --> 00:09:47,130
Great.

152
00:09:47,130 --> 00:09:48,850
Awesome.

153
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,490
Su, have you lost your mind?

154
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:52,640
You'll ruin everyone.

155
00:09:54,010 --> 00:09:54,490
Buddy,

156
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:55,640
I told you.

157
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:57,250
It's all about trust.

158
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,560
If you can't trust me with this,

159
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,610
how can we work together?

160
00:10:00,610 --> 00:10:01,490
How can I trust you?

161
00:10:01,970 --> 00:10:02,850
(Just when I thought)

162
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,040
(our business would keep booming,)

163
00:10:05,850 --> 00:10:06,850
(I overheard)

164
00:10:06,850 --> 00:10:09,040
(him and Lu Xiuyuan arguing.)

165
00:10:09,040 --> 00:10:10,610
Think long-term.

166
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:12,490
Our business will expand, alright?

167
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,610
Look at the accounts.

168
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,850
You're not getting anywhere.

169
00:10:16,850 --> 00:10:17,880
Is that how you see me?

170
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,490
Yes, that's how I see you.

171
00:10:19,490 --> 00:10:20,760
What do buddies rely on?

172
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:21,640
Trust.

173
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,680
If I don't trust you,

174
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,970
I won't be with you.

175
00:10:23,970 --> 00:10:24,760
And?

176
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:25,610
If you trust me,

177
00:10:25,610 --> 00:10:26,640
turn yourself in now.

178
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:29,010
I was kept in the dark like a fool.

179
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,610
I just wanted an honest life

180
00:10:30,610 --> 00:10:31,370
and peace of mind.

181
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:32,560
You're despicable!

182
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,680
Is that what you think of me?

183
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:35,160
- Yes.
- Get out!

184
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,210
Don't ever come back!

185
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:49,680
Mr. Sun.

186
00:10:50,730 --> 00:10:51,800
I missed you so much.

187
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,610
Sit.

188
00:10:52,850 --> 00:10:53,880
- Okay.
- Here.

189
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:57,160
Sorry you had to see that.

190
00:10:57,610 --> 00:10:58,330
People these days

191
00:10:58,330 --> 00:11:00,250
