195
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,880
All thanks to you.

196
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:10,560
I've calculated everything.

197
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,090
Why don't you take a look?

198
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:16,490
No need. I trust you.

199
00:11:16,970 --> 00:11:18,610
That was the last time

200
00:11:18,610 --> 00:11:19,800
I saw Lu Xiuyuan.

201
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,680
The next news I got about him

202
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:22,880
was

203
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,610
his death in the car crash.

204
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:27,970
I swear,

205
00:11:28,610 --> 00:11:29,450
his death

206
00:11:30,010 --> 00:11:31,450
had nothing to do with me.

207
00:11:31,970 --> 00:11:32,520
Nothing?

208
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,490
