217
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:49,730
No.

218
00:11:50,330 --> 00:11:51,250
I wouldn't dare.

219
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:54,010
I'm not as bold as Su Shilun.

220
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,640
So you're saying

221
00:12:01,210 --> 00:12:02,560
my parents' car accident

222
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:05,040
was orchestrated by Su Shilun.

223
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,210
Right?

224
00:12:09,010 --> 00:12:11,640
(I saw Su Shilun get into
Lu Xiuyuan's car.)

225
00:12:18,610 --> 00:12:20,210
(After the fight that night,)

226
00:12:20,610 --> 00:12:22,090
(I saw Su Shilun)

227
00:12:22,090 --> 00:12:23,400
(get into Lu Xiuyuan's car.)

228
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,210
(A few days later,)

229
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:27,800
(news of Lu Xiuyuan's accident came.)

230
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,680
(I thought)

231
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,680
(it must be connected to Su Shilun.)

232
00:13:01,010 --> 00:13:02,210
(But I only suspected it,)

233
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,970
(I have no proof.)

234
00:13:09,610 --> 00:13:10,680
You came here

235
00:13:11,490 --> 00:13:12,680
to sound me out.

236
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:14,640
The one you're after

237
00:13:15,610 --> 00:13:16,610
is Su Shilun.

238
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,850
What does it have to do with you?

239
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,370
Whether I got something to do with it,

240
00:13:25,210 --> 00:13:26,210
you'll only learn

241
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:29,250
the truth from me.

242
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,610
If you want to take down Su Shilun,

243
00:13:35,210 --> 00:13:36,610
I can work with you.

244
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:38,040
Work with me?

245
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:42,210
It's simple.

246
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,210
Once he's gone,

247
00:13:44,450 --> 00:13:45,610
no one

248
00:13:45,850 --> 00:13:47,850
can threaten me anymore.

249
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:48,920
But

250
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:50,370
I have one condition.

251
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:51,970
When it's done,

252
00:13:52,090 --> 00:13:53,210
I want

253
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:54,760
Shilun Gallery.

254
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,400
Who are you to negotiate with me?

255
00:14:01,450 --> 00:14:02,850
Don't try to threaten me.

256
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:04,970
Or you'd have taken it to the police.

257
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:08,450
Judging by the looks of it,

258
00:14:09,010 --> 00:14:11,040
