259
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:14,040
Or you wouldn't come to me.

260
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:17,280
You'd go straight to Su Shilun.

261
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,760
Why should I trust you?

262
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:22,560
I want that gallery

263
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:24,280
for the land it's on.

264
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,800
I want to build a resort.

265
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:28,280
I already

266
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:30,010
talked to Ms. Qin about it.

267
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:34,450
She turned me down.

268
00:14:37,970 --> 00:14:39,970
If I help you with Su Shilun,

269
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:41,970
besides the gallery,

270
00:14:42,610 --> 00:14:45,210
the rest of Shilun Group is yours.

271
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:46,970
What do you think?

272
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,160
(After the fight that night,)

273
00:14:52,490 --> 00:14:55,040
(I saw Su Shilun
get into Lu Xiuyuan's car.)

274
00:14:56,210 --> 00:14:57,490
(A few days later,)

275
00:14:57,490 --> 00:14:59,250
