276
00:14:59,850 --> 00:15:02,280
(I thought
it must be connected to Su Shilun.)

277
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:06,160
(Lu Xiuyuan was the only one)

278
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:08,160
(who knew
about my dealings with Su Shilun.)

279
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:10,040
(This morning,)

280
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:12,250
(local entrepreneur
Lu Xiuyuan and his wife,)

281
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:14,760
