(to have him killed,)

286
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,160
(right?)

287
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:28,040
(No. I wouldn't dare.)

288
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,610
(I'm not as bold as Su Shilun.)

289
00:15:35,450 --> 00:15:36,250
Let me tell you.

290
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:39,160
If you want to take from the Su family,

291
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,970
I need to see
what you're truly capable of.

292
00:15:47,450 --> 00:15:48,640
I can work with you

293
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,640
to bring down Su Shilun.

294
00:15:51,210 --> 00:15:52,210
(Only I can)

295
00:15:52,450 --> 00:15:55,010
(reveal some truths to you.)

296
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:10,850
Sun Yiming.

297
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:12,800
I agree.

298
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:28,370
He agreed so quickly.

299
00:16:30,970 --> 00:16:32,400
Is he playing me?

300
00:16:35,847 --> 00:16:44,747
(Art World Grenade! Genius Artist L
Goes Public With Gallery Manager)

301
00:16:56,250 --> 00:16:56,880
Mr. Sun.

302
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,400
You seem in a bad mood today.

303
00:17:02,010 --> 00:17:03,090
Who are you?

304
00:17:03,490 --> 00:17:05,080
Someone who can help you.

305
00:17:07,010 --> 00:17:08,520
What I have here

306
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,760
is Shilun Group's

307
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:11,600
weaknesses.

308
00:17:13,840 --> 00:17:15,890
Once he's deep in debt,

309
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:17,600
you

310
00:17:18,840 --> 00:17:20,800
can easily crush Su Shilun.

311
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,080
By then,

312
00:17:22,970 --> 00:17:25,360
you can ask for the gallery as payment.

313
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:29,010
Why should I trust you?

314
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:31,400
It doesn't matter

315
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,250
whether you trust me.

316
00:17:33,210 --> 00:17:34,970
What matters

317
00:17:34,970 --> 00:17:36,360
is whether you've got the guts.

318
00:17:46,697 --> 00:17:51,497
(Shilun Group Financial Debt Report)

319
00:18:18,297 --> 00:18:19,752
(Sun Yiming)

320
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:22,360
Ms. Qin.

321
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:24,450
I called to ask you again

322
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,280
whether you still refuse
to sell the gallery.

323
00:18:26,410 --> 00:18:27,280
Mr. Sun.

324
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,560
No matter how many times you ask,

325
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:29,970
my answer is no.

326
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:33,010
What a pity then.

327
00:18:33,210 --> 00:18:35,760
But nothing is always absolute.

328
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,560
What do you think?

329
00:18:53,210 --> 00:18:54,010
Hello?

330
00:18:55,210 --> 00:18:56,120
Lu Li.

331
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:57,280
Are you home?

332
00:18:57,890 --> 00:18:59,080
I'm not home.

333
00:18:59,080 --> 00:18:59,690
I'm outside.

334
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:00,560
I'll head back soon.

335
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:03,800
I'm feeling down.

336
00:19:04,450 --> 00:19:05,970
Can I wait at your place?

337
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:08,490
Sure, wait for me.

338
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:50,650
You're back.

339
00:19:53,650 --> 00:19:54,600
How much did you drink?

340
00:19:55,650 --> 00:19:56,600
Your face is all red.

341
00:19:58,890 --> 00:19:59,690
Not much.

342
00:20:07,690 --> 00:20:08,690
What's wrong?

343
00:20:08,690 --> 00:20:09,600
You're upset.

344
00:20:11,650 --> 00:20:13,210
I met someone a few days ago.

345
00:20:15,730 --> 00:20:16,840
It put me in a bad mood.

346
00:20:18,250 --> 00:20:18,730
Who?

347
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,320
Who upset you?

348
00:20:30,490 --> 00:20:32,450
Su Shilun's biggest rival.

349
00:20:34,450 --> 00:20:35,600
His name is Sun Yiming.

350
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,450
You probably don't know him.

351
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:43,080
What's up?

352
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:45,800
He wanted me to sell the gallery to him.

353
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:50,410
He said he could help me
get everything I want.

354
00:20:51,930 --> 00:20:52,690
And?

355
00:20:52,690 --> 00:20:54,320
There's no way I'd agree.

356
00:20:57,010 --> 00:20:57,840
Lu Li.

357
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:00,520
Do you know

358
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:03,490
what that gallery means to me?

359
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:09,730
It's my mom's blood, sweat and tears.

360
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,970
I saw how much

361
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:14,280
she sacrificed for it,

362
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,730
but Su Shilun made it his

363
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,080
and shamelessly

364
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,690
put his own name on it.

365
00:21:28,010 --> 00:21:29,450
It's the only place

366
00:21:31,730 --> 00:21:34,040
where I can quietly miss her.

367
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:46,930
That's why

368
00:21:48,010 --> 00:21:50,250
I'll protect it with all I have.

369
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:55,450
No one can take it from me.

370
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:58,250
One day,

371
00:21:58,840 --> 00:22:01,080
I'll even reclaim the name.

372
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:15,600
You'll help me, right?

373
00:22:36,010 --> 00:22:36,840
I'm always here.

374
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:40,730
It's all done.

375
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:44,120
Good.

376
00:22:45,890 --> 00:22:47,080
Shilun Group

377
00:22:47,760 --> 00:22:49,250
looks shiny on the outside,

378
00:22:50,040 --> 00:22:51,450
but it's actually full of holes

379
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:53,250
and falling apart.

380
00:22:57,210 --> 00:22:58,250
Tell me.

381
00:22:59,170 --> 00:22:59,970
How did Lu Li

382
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:01,800
end up colluding with Sun Yiming?

383
00:23:03,650 --> 00:23:05,120
Does Qin Yuebai

384
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:06,520
have such poor taste?

385
00:23:07,730 --> 00:23:08,890
I'm not sure.

386
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:11,250
But Sun Yiming doesn't seem

387
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:14,520
to trust Lu Li.

388
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:23,320
Then

389
00:23:24,690 --> 00:23:26,650
we can make good use

390
00:23:26,650 --> 00:23:27,800
of Lu Li.

391
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:32,210
Whatever you say.

392
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,040
Sun Yiming.

393
00:23:36,320 --> 00:23:37,410
What are you trying to do?

394
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:39,280
I told you.

395
00:23:39,930 --> 00:23:41,040
I want that gallery.

396
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,800
What did we agree on?

397
00:23:44,040 --> 00:23:46,120
Who are we teaming up against?

398
00:23:46,280 --> 00:23:47,600
Su Shilun, right?

399
00:23:47,650 --> 00:23:48,840
I'm a businessman.

400
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,250
Business is business.

401
00:23:52,250 --> 00:23:53,600
When cash is on the table,

402
00:23:53,650 --> 00:23:55,080
who wouldn't take it?

403
00:23:55,280 --> 00:23:56,930
What's that got to do with Yuebai?

404
00:23:58,250 --> 00:23:59,080
The gallery

405
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,840
is under Qin Yuebai's name.

406
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:02,250
If I don't pressure her,

407
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,210
who should I pressure?

408
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:11,800
Lu Li.

409
00:24:12,450 --> 00:24:14,040
I'll give you a word of advice.

410
00:24:14,650 --> 00:24:15,800
Don't let your fury rule you.

411
00:24:17,650 --> 00:24:19,600
Don't betray your parents

412
00:24:20,650 --> 00:24:22,040
for the daughter of your enemy.

413
00:24:24,040 --> 00:24:25,210
Now that I've said it,

414
00:24:25,450 --> 00:24:26,600
think it over.

415
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:05,930
You're awake.

416
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,360
Your apron

417
00:25:10,690 --> 00:25:11,840
is pretty cute.

418
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:21,520
What a feast.

419
00:25:22,450 --> 00:25:24,010
I didn't know you can cook.

420
00:25:25,490 --> 00:25:26,690
I just think

421
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:29,450
we haven't sat down for a meal

422
00:25:29,450 --> 00:25:30,450
in a long time.

423
00:25:31,650 --> 00:25:32,730
That's true.

424
00:25:40,840 --> 00:25:41,800
Yummy.

425
00:25:43,010 --> 00:25:44,450
I didn't expect you to cook so well.

426
00:25:44,930 --> 00:25:45,600
From now on,

427
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:46,800
you have to cook more often.

428
00:25:55,210 --> 00:25:56,040
Yuebai.

429
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:58,410
What is it?

430
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:07,760
Yuebai, actually...

431
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:09,210
I...

432
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:11,600
Hold on.

433
00:26:15,730 --> 00:26:16,170
Hello?

434
00:26:16,170 --> 00:26:16,720
Hello, Ms. Qin

435
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,690
Bad news,
something happened at the gallery.

436
00:26:19,410 --> 00:26:20,450
What happened?

437
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:22,010
Sun Yiming came to seize the gallery.

438
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:24,840
Something happened.

439
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:34,690
Baoyan

440
00:26:36,080 --> 00:26:37,730
really caused me big trouble.

441
00:26:37,930 --> 00:26:39,600
It allowed Sun Yiming to take advantage!

442
00:26:45,010 --> 00:26:48,840
Maybe we can't keep the gallery anymore.

443
00:26:51,010 --> 00:26:52,650
The gallery is where you started.

444
00:27:18,890 --> 00:27:20,080
What I mean is

445
00:27:24,930 --> 00:27:26,010
if this matter

446
00:27:26,410 --> 00:27:28,410
gets out to gossipers,

447
00:27:29,250 --> 00:27:31,010
they'll make a big fuss out of it.

448
00:27:31,690 --> 00:27:32,970
I'm worried

449
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:34,730
about our stock price

450
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,890
and Yuebai.

451
00:27:38,890 --> 00:27:39,690
Enough.

452
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:47,280
I'll talk to Sun Yiming again.

453
00:27:48,890 --> 00:27:50,450
See if there's a way to fix this.

454
00:27:54,210 --> 00:27:55,170
I can't believe

455
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:58,080
I haven't finished sorting out this mess.

456
00:27:59,840 --> 00:28:00,930
I really spoiled

457
00:28:01,410 --> 00:28:03,040
that girl.

458
00:28:32,385 --> 00:28:35,322
(Shilun Gallery Acquisition Agreement)

459
00:28:47,835 --> 00:28:50,347
(Party A: Sun Yiming,
Party B: Shilun Group)

460
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:08,930
Sun Yiming must've pulled some tricks

461
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:10,520
to strike a deal with Su Shilun.

462
00:29:10,890 --> 00:29:12,040
He must've held a grudge

463
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:13,450
after I rejected him.

464
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,600
Did you see him
at the gallery yesterday?

465
00:29:17,010 --> 00:29:17,840
No.

466
00:29:18,730 --> 00:29:19,650
Do you know him?

467
00:29:20,890 --> 00:29:21,450
I've

468
00:29:21,650 --> 00:29:22,840
only seen him in magazines.

469
00:29:25,010 --> 00:29:25,800
Yuebai.

470
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:28,450
Calm things down first.

471
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:30,650
I'll figure out what happened.

472
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:32,600
Okay.

473
00:29:51,141 --> 00:29:55,741
♪When I wandered
into your still, deep night♪

474
00:29:56,301 --> 00:30:02,541
♪I could never forget
that sky full of stars♪

475
00:30:04,938 --> 00:30:10,021
♪Time sketched between every stroke♪

476
00:30:10,438 --> 00:30:16,621
♪Because you were by my side,
I let all my guards fall♪

477
00:30:16,738 --> 00:30:18,188
♪The disguise♪

478
00:30:33,461 --> 00:30:36,788
♪You are my tender♪

479
00:30:36,838 --> 00:30:39,813
♪You are my sender♪

480
00:30:40,251 --> 00:30:47,076
♪All my inspiration
is lit by this warmth♪

481
00:30:47,613 --> 00:30:51,226
♪You are my tender♪

482
00:30:51,351 --> 00:30:54,526
♪You are my defender♪

483
00:30:54,738 --> 00:30:58,926
♪I drift past the winds
and anchor in your sea♪

484
00:30:59,101 --> 00:31:02,351
♪Let time carry me far away♪

485
00:31:02,451 --> 00:31:06,788
♪Tender♪
